Happy Birthday, my boy!🎶
Every time I try to write something about you, words fall short—and maybe that’s because you mean more than words can hold. Though, if you’re here on my feed, you already know how particular I am about that but this is how much you mean to me… 😛 And today, I’ll try anyway.

T, watching you grow has been one of the most beautiful things. No matter what life has thrown at you, you’ve always pushed through—with strength, grace, and that quiet (not quite, but a lot..) fire in you. And just look at you now. I’m so proud of the person you’re becoming.

These 6 years of knowing eachother & going through all the ups & downs had been crazy but…. Thank you—for being my one-call-away, for being my chaos buddy, for showing up when it matters most, and for making me feel safe in a world that sometimes doesn’t.

You make me proud. Always.
Love you endlessly. 🤎
Happy Birthday again, T. Here’s to many more memories. 🧿✨ @kayde_main
